{"tier":5,"question":"What is financialization?","answer":"The increasing dominance of financial activities and motives in the economy relative to production","choices":["The adoption of digital payment systems","The increasing dominance of financial activities and motives in the economy relative to production","The shift from manufacturing to services","The growing influence of central banks on economic policy"]},
